      :- blawx_ultimately(-legal_basis(X)), blawx_becomes(legal_basis(X),datetime(Start)),
      blawx_not_interrupted(datetime(Start),-legal_basis(X),datetime(eot)).\nblawx_during(datetime(bot),-legal_basis(X),datetime(eot))
      :- blawx_initially(-legal_basis(X)), blawx_ultimately(-legal_basis(X)), blawx_becomes(-legal_basis(X),datetime(Start)),
      blawx_not_interrupted(datetime(bot),-legal_basis(X),datetime(eot)).\nlegal_basis(consent).\nlegal_basis(contract)."
